                   Salesforce Apex Coding

----------------------------------------------------------------          
          
                 Date and Time in Apex Coding
          
----------------------------------------------------------------

Coding :

public class DateandTime {
    public static void date()
    {
        Date todayy = Date.newInstance(2022,04,30);
        Time timenow = Time.newInstance(02,30,00,00);
        DateTime datime = DateTime.newInstance(2022,04,30,02,30,00);
        
        system.debug(todayy);
        system.debug(timenow);
        system.debug(datime);
    }

}
----------------------------------------------------------------

To Execute :

DateandTime.date();

----------------------------------------------------------------
